    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that sounds like a good start. can u expand on the \"impeccable grooming and dress codes\" part? like, what are the actual standards for looking professional and sophisticated in an international business context? i want to give my readers some concrete rules to follow so they dont make any mistakes.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
