    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense for a corporate look. but what about when people are in places like india, or parts of africa or southeast asia? like, if i'm at a high-end business dinner in mumbai or jakarta, is wearing a western suit still the only way to look \"sophisticated\"? or are there other ways to be professional there that aren't just \"westernized\"?",
